%% MLflow Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.3/mlflow.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Client<br/>(SDK/CLI)
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant AuthMW as K8s Auth Middleware
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking (Authenticated Request)
    Client->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward request (HTTP/5000)<br/>Headers: x-remote-user, x-remote-groups
    MLflow->>AuthMW: Check authorization
    AuthMW->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>resource: experiments<br/>group: mlflow.kubeflow.org
    K8sAPI-->>AuthMW: Allowed/Denied
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run metadata<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Success
    MLflow-->>Proxy: JSON Response
    Proxy-->>Client: 200 OK + Run data

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Upload
    Client->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/5000)
    MLflow->>AuthMW: Check authorization
    AuthMW->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>AuthMW: Allowed
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Access Key<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow-->>Client: Upload confirmed

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Workspace Resolution
    Client->>MLflow: Request with X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE header
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: Verify namespace exists<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Namespace confirmed

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: OpenTelemetry Trace Ingestion
    participant OTel as OTel Collector/SDK
    OTel->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>OTLP/HTTP format<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MLflow->>AuthMW: Check authorization (experiments/update)
    AuthMW->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>AuthMW: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: Store trace spans<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Success
    MLflow-->>OTel: 200 OK
